name: AND
body:
### AND.
AND is another name daemon, or an Apache-licensed Named Daemon, or something else.

It's a progression from the thoughts I had when failing to write, R Squared.

A prototype is now appearing in its own repo: [andns-prototype](https://github.com/nicdoye/andns-prototype).

The code in here may be abandoned, replaced, or used. I don't know.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
